{"data":[{"date":"14:05 09/07","title":"L\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean CLB nh\u00ed Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb k\u1eb9t trong hang","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/lang-bong-da-dong-vien-clb-nhi-thai-lan-bi-ket-trong-hang.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4089","checkdouble":"190769"},{"date":"15:25 09/07","title":"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 tri\u1ec7u ph\u00fa s\u1edf h\u1eefu chu\u1ed7i si\u00eau th\u1ecb","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/trong-tai-world-cup-2018-la-trieu-phu-so-huu-chuoi-sieu-thi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bjorn Kuipers - tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e1ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea3 trong l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Bjorn Kuipers - tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c C\u0110V t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00f4ng tin nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n sau khi c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Anh h\u00f4m 7/7 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u00f4ng t\u00e2m, Bjorn Kuipers c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec7u ph\u00fa. \u00d4ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ed1i t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Samara.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Bjorn Kuipers d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Bjorn Kuipers d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tri\u1ec7u ph\u00fa Kuipers l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u1eefa Nga v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKuipers sinh t\u1ea1i Oldenzaal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1973. \u00d4ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p khoa kinh doanh \u1edf Radboud Nijmegen - m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc danh ti\u1ebfng \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0. Sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m b\u00f4n ba l\u1eadp nghi\u1ec7p, \"v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en\" ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean Jumbo - m\u1ed9t chu\u1ed7i si\u00eau th\u1ecb b\u00e1n l\u1ebb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng tr\u1ea3i kh\u1eafp x\u1ee9 s\u1edf hoa tulip.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb The Sun, doanh thu trong n\u0103m 2016 t\u1eeb ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kinh doanh c\u1ee7a Bjorn Kuipers l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 11,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i Harry Kane (5,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/n\u0103m). Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \"tay tr\u00e1i\" l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, m\u1ed9t quan ch\u1ee9c UEFA c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng nu\u00f4i s\u1ed1ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn kho\u1ea3n thu t\u1eeb chu\u1ed7i si\u00eau th\u1ecb \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBjorn Kuipers l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n FIFA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2006. \u00d4ng l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea3 trong l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Kuipers t\u1eebng c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Italy \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2014. 4 n\u0103m sau t\u1ea1i Nga, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sinh n\u0103m 1973 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \"n\u1edf m\u00e0y n\u1edf m\u1eb7t\" khi gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Bjorn Kuipers \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng \u1edf 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. N\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a \"Tam s\u01b0\" tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u1ede c\u1ea3 4 l\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, \"v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en\" ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfng n\u00e0o.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4088","checkdouble":"190777"},{"date":"17:37 09/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore 19h00 ng\u00e0y 9/7 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Real Madrid vs Betis: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Betis v\u00f2ng 27 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG T\u00e2y Ban Nha TBN La Liga 2016/17 l\u00fac 02h45 ng\u00e0y 13/3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\n- U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 c\u00f3 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a U19 Indonesia, U19 Myanmar, U19 Philippines v\u00e0 U19 Brunei.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 v\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 so v\u1edbi U19 Indonesia v\u00e0 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. Sau 4 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi c\u00f3 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u00edt h\u01a1n 2 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 3 v\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eadm U19 Singapore, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi hy v\u1ecdng U19 Indonesia d\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore 19h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 97 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore 19h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 97 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-01-u19-indonesia-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong kh\u00e2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ch\u00ednh HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi U19 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 U19 Indonesia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 U19 Singapore. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-0. 1 n\u0103m sau, d\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1edbi Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh\u2026, nh\u01b0ng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 0-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4087","checkdouble":"190790"},{"date":"14:30 09/07","title":"L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Angel di Maria","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/12/28/lo-ben-do-moi-cua-angel-di-maria.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Napoli mua Angel Di Maria c\u1ee7a PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Di Maria s\u1eafp h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Angel Di Maria v\u1edbi PSG ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Napoli mua Angel Di Maria \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Napoli mua Angel Di Maria \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/Chi-35-trieu-bang,-Napoli-mua-Angel-Di-Maria-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Di Maria ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Di Maria \u0111\u00e3 ghi 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 30 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ligue 1. Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i anh ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho b\u1ed9 ba Mbappe, Neymar v\u00e0 Cavani. Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn khi Neymar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng Di Maria m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDi Maria ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, song PSG kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ngo\u00e0i b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Mbappe, Neymar v\u00e0 Cavani, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Julian Draxler.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThay v\u00ec gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Di Maria th\u00ec PSG ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Di Maria</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli mua Angel Di Maria c\u1ee7a PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Di Maria chuan bi toi Barca\" title=\"Di Maria chuan bi toi Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/28/lo-ben-do-moi-cua-angel-di-maria.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Di Maria&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Mediaset Premium kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e2n HLV Carlo Ancelotti c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo mu\u1ed1n \u0111o\u00e0n t\u1ee5 v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf Italia, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nhau \u1edf Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNapoli mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Di Maria, m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a anh s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn 5 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Ngo\u00e0i Napoli th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/psg-chot-gia-ban-sao-khung-cho-chuyen-nhuong-barca-172-176377.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Di Maria</span>, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Napoli c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf, b\u1edfi PSG \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y kinh ph\u00ed n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4086","checkdouble":"190767"},{"date":"15:11 09/07","title":"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c: PSG chi 270 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/12/psg-chi-270-trieu-euro-mua-coutinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Philippe Coutinho c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 270 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 ba Cavani, Neymar v\u00e0 PSG khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i. Ngo\u00e0i tam t\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Angel di Maria v\u00e0 Julian Draxler.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Philippe Coutinho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 270 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Philippe Coutinho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 270 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/PSG-muon-mua-Philippe-Coutinho-voi-gia-270-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Thomas Tuchel mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a PSG kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. Ngo\u00e0i Marco Verratti th\u00ec nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Adrien Rabiot hay Thiago Motta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao. \u0110\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111ang nh\u1eafm r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU, Luka Modric c\u1ee7a Real Madrid hay Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Coutinho l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mundo Deportivo, PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Philippe Coutinho c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 270 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c PSG chi 270 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c PSG chi 270 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Cuc-soc-PSG-chi-270-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-Barca-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Coutinho\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Coutinho, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n PSG chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i. Coutinho m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay t\u1eeb Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 160 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 400 tri\u1ec7u euro, song PSG tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 270 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar, ng\u01b0\u1eddi gia nh\u1eadp PSG m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Coutinho v\u00e0 PSG \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ef1u sao Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p chi 270 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Coutinho, PSG s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh vi ph\u1ea1m Lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. C\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng Mbappe s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i, Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 290 tri\u1ec7u euro si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/psg-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-buffon-197-190549.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Buffon</span> theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 40 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4085","checkdouble":"190772"},{"date":"16:46 09/07","title":"Xavi ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft anh ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t k\u1ebf th\u1eeba Julen Lopetegui.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. B\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Julen Lopetegui k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng qua c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ea1nh tay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau khi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Lopetegui s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Real h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp kh\u1ea9n. Sau khi tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 40 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Porto.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-HLV-Tay-Ban-Nha-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nFernando Hierro l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean ch\u00e8o l\u00e1i \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c La Roja \u0111i t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Nga sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Xavi kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec Enrique \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau World Cup 2018, Hierro t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5t nh\u1eafc l\u00ean l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. RFEF d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd m\u1eddi Luis Enrique ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u00f2n tr\u1ed1ng sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u1ea5p cao s\u00e1ng nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xavi va Messi\" title=\"Xavi va Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Xavi kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec b\u1ecb \u0110T\u00a0TBN ng\u00f3 l\u01a1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Anh kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 b\u1edfi tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng\u201d, Xavi n\u00f3i v\u1edbi AS. \u201cTh\u1ee9 2, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 3, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi gh\u1ebf HLV \u0110TQG. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi th\u00eam, ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-fernando-hierro-roi-ghe-hlv-truong-cua-tbn-421-190705.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Fernando Hierro r\u1eddi gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-466-190435.html\">World Cup 2018: 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bi-co-the-dan-dat-tay-ban-nha-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190427.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ky-world-cup-cua-tay-ban-nha-khong-te-nhu-nguoi-ta-nghi-421-190397.html\">K\u1ef3 World Cup c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ngh\u0129</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4084","checkdouble":"190785"},{"date":"14:47 09/07","title":"B\u1ecb gh\u1ebb l\u1ea1nh, Joe Hart quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111o\u1ea1n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/17/joe-hart-sap-chia-tay-man-city-sau-12-nam-gan-bo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Joe Hart r\u1eddi Man City \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n thay v\u00ec theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n nh\u01b0 trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Joe Hart quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joe Hart \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u00ea th\u1ea3m khi HLV Pep Guardiola ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Man City. T\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ecb Pep gh\u1ebb l\u1ea1nh, Joe Hart r\u1eddi Man City \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ecb Pep gh\u1ebb l\u1ea1nh, Joe Hart r\u1eddi Man City \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/8/Bi-Pep-ghe-lanh,-Joe-Hart-roi-Man-City-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Joe Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Pep \u1edf Man City, Joe Hart b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi Torino theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi West Ham. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Joe Hart \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Man City.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, Joe Hart r\u1eddi Man City \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n thay v\u00ec theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n nh\u01b0 trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPep quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Hart, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n. Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man xanh gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t, anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n thay v\u00ec theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Joe Hart bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u quan t\u00e2m Joe Hart, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia, Ph\u00e1p hay T\u00e2y Ban Nha. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-doi-bong-dau-tien-bi-joe-hart-tu-choi-172-187424.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sporting Lisbon mu\u1ed1n mua Hart</span>, song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Joe Hart\" title=\"thu mon Joe Hart\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/6/HLV-DT-Anh-tiet-lo-thu-mon-bat-chinh-truoc-Lithuania-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Joe Hart bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i NHA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nWolvehampton v\u00e0 Watford \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 8 \u0111\u1ebfn 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Song \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y Hart bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Man City, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Joe Hart s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n. M\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u01a1ng duy\u00ean k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 12 n\u0103m gi\u1eefa th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u00e0 Man xanh d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4083","checkdouble":"190768"},{"date":"16:31 09/07","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng Ligue 1 bay t\u1edbi London k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/21/jeanmichael-bay-toi-london-ky-hop-dong-voi-dai-gia-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo France Football c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jean-Michael Seri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Jean-Michael Seri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nice. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi\u1ebfn anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/26/Jean-Michael-Seri-ky-hop-dong-voi-Chelsea-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jean Michael Seri c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf NHA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-arsenal-va-chelsea-dang-dam-phan-voi-napoli-172-188308.html\" target=\"_blank\">Napoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Jean-Michael Seri</span>, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Nice.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Napoli ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Michael Seri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo France Football c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng\u00a0v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFrance Football kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Nice \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea b\u1ecf ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Michael Seri</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Michael Seri, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal, Chelsea, Fulham v\u00e0 West Ham. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jean-Michael Seri la cau thu sang gia nhat cua Nice mua truoc\" title=\"Jean-Michael Seri l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nice m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/21/jeanmichael-bay-toi-london-ky-hop-dong-voi-dai-gia-premier-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jean-Michael Seri\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1eafp thay th\u1ebf Conte \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Michael Seri, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 v\u1edbi Nice ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Michael Seri t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Michael Seri s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4082","checkdouble":"190782"},{"date":"16:43 09/07","title":"Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Daniel Sturridge","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/26/klopp-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-daniel-sturridge.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Daniel Sturridge, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Daniel Sturridge ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Daniel Sturridge th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Khi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Roberto Firmino. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Daniel Sturridge h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Daniel Sturridge h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/26/klopp-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-daniel-sturridge.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sturridge ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y Sturridge t\u1edbi West Brom theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 \u0110\u00f4ng v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Daniel Sturridge \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Liverpool ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, \u1edf Anh West Ham, Wolves v\u00e0 Watford mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Sturridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-tiet-lo-su-thuc-dau-long-tu-sturridge-172-189649.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua Sturridge</span>, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Sturridge</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Daniel Sturridge, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp va Sturridge\" title=\"HLV Klopp va Sturridge\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/2/Thang-Bayern-3-0-HLV-Jurgen-Klopp-van-khong-hai-long-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp s\u1ebd trao th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Sturridge</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNgo\u00e0i Firmino, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu 4 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c, bao g\u1ed3m Danny Ings, Dominic Solanke, Divock Origi v\u00e0 Daniel Sturridge, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi ri\u00eang tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Sturridge, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t hay kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Sturridge l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ed1t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u00edch v\u1edbi Liverpool. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t Sturridge s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4081","checkdouble":"190783"},{"date":"16:48 09/07","title":"N\u00d3NG: Hai ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/nong-hai-ngoi-sao-den-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1eady t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o David Ornstein c\u1ee7a t\u1edd BBC th\u00ec CLB Arsenal v\u1eeba \u0111\u00f3n 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 9/7.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;V\u00e0 sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mang t\u00ean Stephan Lichtsteiner, Bernd Leno v\u00e0 Sokratis Papastathopoulos, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ti\u1ebfp theo.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Torreira va Matteo Guendouzi sap cap ben Arsenal\" title=\"Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/lucas-torreira-972041-15288579744461655481829.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Lucas Torreira (tr\u00e1i) v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi (ph\u1ea3i) s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian qua v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u CLB bao g\u1ed3m: ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Uruguay, Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U20 Ph\u00e1p, Matteo Guendouzi.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Torreira n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB Sampdoria t\u1ea1i Seria A, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Uruguay tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018. Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Unai Emery.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Guendouzi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 19 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p s\u1edf h\u1eefu. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb tay c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Tottenham v\u00e0 M.U, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi cho CLB Lorient s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo BBC, c\u1ea3 hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i London \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Arsenal. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o x\u1ea3y ra, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng The Gunners s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 hai h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4080","checkdouble":"190784"},{"date":"17:53 09/07","title":"Alex Sandro \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/alex-sandro-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-hau-ve-trai-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Sandro \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. C\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcos Alonso (Chelsea)</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Marcos Alonso l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 3-5-2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Conte v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 cho th\u1ea5y anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Sandro N\u00ean hay kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Sandro N\u00ean hay kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/MU-muon-mua-Alex-Sandro-Nen-hay-khong-nen-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcos Alonso</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMarcos Alonso l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t Premier League 2017/18, anh c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 7 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m rung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Alex Sandro c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 8 trong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, Sandro l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. 75% s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Alonso l\u00e0 70%. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Sandro c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Alonso (44 so v\u1edbi 16).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, Sandro t\u1ea1o ra 27 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 4 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi Alonso, anh t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 34 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i, Alonso (1m88) kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Sandro (1m80). C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u00f3 61 l\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 38.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andrew Robertson (Liverpool)</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng Andrew Robertson \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng vi\u1ec7c Alberto Moreno d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp b\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andrew Robertson\" title=\"Andrew Robertson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/robertson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andrew Robertson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi Alex Sandro, Andrew Robertson ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n (1 so v\u1edbi 4), nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i anh l\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o h\u01a1n (5 so v\u1edbi 4).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra 21 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng 5 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n ho\u00e1n th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Sandro t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 27 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&nbsp;\u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Robertson l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u1ee9 2 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, Sandro ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi Robertson (27 so v\u1edbi 26), nh\u01b0ng n\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n g\u1ea7n 200 ph\u00fat (2115 ph\u00fat so v\u1edbi 1943 ph\u00fat).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ben Davies (Tottenham)</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Ben Davies ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Danny Rose m\u1edbi l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Tottenham. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mauricio Pochettino tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ben Davies\" title=\"Ben Davies\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/ben-davies.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ben Davies</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Ben Davies kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Alex Sandro (2 so v\u1edbi 4), nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o anh l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i (6 so v\u1edbi 4). Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 47 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi 27 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Ben Davies ch\u1ec9 22 l\u1ea7n m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, so v\u1edbi 44 c\u1ee7a Sandro l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-o-vi-tri-hau-ve-trai-172-182680.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Sandro</span>, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ryan Bertrand (Southampton)</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ryan Bertrand l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o sau 35 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Premier League 2017/18, khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh con s\u1ed1 4 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Sandro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ryan Bentrand\" title=\"Ryan Bentrand\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/bentrand.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ryan Bentrand</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, c\u1ea3 Ryan Bertrand v\u00e0 Sandro \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, song ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Southampton t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n (36 so v\u1edbi 27).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 Bertrand v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Sandro. C\u1ef1u sao Chelsea c\u00f3 34 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 43 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 27 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 23 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nacho Monreal (Arsenal)</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nacho Monreal \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Monreal\" title=\"Monreal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/16/hlv-wenger-monreal-khong-con-la-mot-hau-ve-trai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nacho Monreal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ghi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 21 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Sandro (4 b\u00e0n sau 17 l\u1ea7n k\u1ebft th\u00fac). V\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, Monreal ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra 14 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, kh\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n so v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus (27 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, 4&nbsp;ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 27 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, song v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n Monreal v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1edbi 49 so v\u1edbi 23.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n*Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4079","checkdouble":"190792"},{"date":"10:27 09/07","title":"Fernandinho b\u1ecb d\u1ecda gi\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi trong tr\u1eadn Brazil thua B\u1ec9","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/fernandinho-bi-doa-giet-vi-ban-phan-luoi-trong-tran-brazil-thua-bi.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4078","checkdouble":"190755"},{"date":"10:38 09/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc c\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec h\u1ecdc sinh h\u1ecdc th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/truong-hoc-cam-bong-da-vi-hoc-sinh-hoc-thoi-an-va-cua-neymar.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2> M\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u00e3 ban b\u1ed1 l\u1ec7nh c\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua v\u00ec t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ed1 b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb xem World Cup qua truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc c\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec h\u1ecdc sinh b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc c\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00ec h\u1ecdc sinh b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/1_4.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc Home Farm s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sportbible, tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc Home Farm t\u1ea1i Colchester, Anh \u0111\u00e3 ban b\u1ed1 l\u1ec7nh c\u1ea5m m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong c\u00e1c gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao b\u1edfi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\u1ecdc sinh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n tranh c\u00e3i, x\u00f4 x\u00e1t nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t \u00fd th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng &quot;tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1&quot; c\u1ee7a Neymar: &quot;\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u em h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i, t\u1eeb 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 11 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft em n\u00e0o c\u0169ng l\u00e0m theo c\u1eadu ta&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch c\u00e1c em v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2n ch\u00ednh&quot;, ban gi\u00e1m hi\u1ec7u nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 huynh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1ee9ng nh\u01b0ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u00fd ki\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. H\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng con em c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00f2a chung v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dau an tai World Cup cua Neymar la 2 ban thang cung vo so pha an va.\" title=\"D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u1ee7a Neymar l\u00e0 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 pha \u0103n v\u1ea1.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/3_1.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u1ee7a Neymar l\u00e0 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 pha \u0103n v\u1ea1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u0111ang lan truy\u1ec1n \u0111o\u1ea1n video c\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f4 vang &quot;Neymar&quot;, c\u00e1c em s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c n\u1eb1m ra s\u00e2n la h\u00e9t v\u1edbi v\u1ebb \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ronaldo &quot;b\u00e9o&quot; kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i: &quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y d\u00e0nh cho Neymar. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3u c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1eadp. Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1eefng trang tin c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd&quot;, Sky Sports d\u1eabn l\u1eddi Ronaldo &quot;b\u00e9o&quot;.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4077","checkdouble":"190756"}]}